_sText:
- aim_usp-aztec-beta -

- both teams spawns with USP, HE, full armor and nightvision.

- as im working on a remake of aztec from cs 1.6 i thought it would be fun to try and make a fun/fy/ba/aim map with a part of the map, mostly for show and hopefully some feedback.

- it seems to be fairly playable, atleast up to 16 players "32 spawnpoints", it can get crowded since most of the action is in one spot, still its just for show.

- this map is made solely out of looking at screenshots taken from cs 1.6

- hopefully ill get the entire map done someday.

- hope you enjoy it!

- oh and might be a good idea to have flashlight enabled, well, depends on your settings.
